'''''Star Wars Insider'' 90''' is the 68th issue of ''[[Star Wars Insider]]'', released in [[October]] [[2006]].

==Contents==
*"[[The Models of Revenge of the Sith, Part 1|The Models of ''Revenge of the Sith'' Part 1]]" {{C|by [[Frank Parisi]]}}
*:<small>The first of a three-part series in which Brian Gernano, head of ILM's Model Shop for Episodes II and III, details how the worlds of ''Revenge of the Sith'' were brought to life. This issue, Gernand shows how he and his team helped build Kashyyyk.</small>
*"[[Aliens of Episode III]]" {{C|by [[Daniel Wallace]]}}
*:<small>''Insider'' speaks with various concept artists and sculptors about how they created the Utapauns, Mustafarians, and Polis Massans, featuring concept art and behind-the-scenes images supplemented with in-universe origins of each species.</small>
*"[[Spaceballs: The Article!]]" {{C|by [[David Maddox]] and [[Rich Handley]], illustrated by [[Randy Martinez]]}}
*:<small>2006 marks the 19th anniversary of ''Spaceballs: The Movie'' (no, that's not a typo) and ''Insider'' catches up with many of the the film's actors to get their recollections of working on the most madcap ''Star Wars'' "fan film" of all.</small>
*"[[Cool Trooper: The Star Wars Art of Nathan Cabrera|Cool Trooper: The ''Star Wars'' Art of Nathan Cabrera]]" {{C|by [[Bonnie Burton]]}}
*:<small>Nathan Cabrera's life-sized Tusken Raider and Stormtrooper Chick sculptures will re-define the way you look at your favorite ''Star Wars'' icons.</small>

